When do you use sections to organize table and collection view controllers? What advantages do sections offer?\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\qr\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf0 >> Sections are used to organize both table and view controllers in situations where the developer wants to organize sets of items by something with a header. This could be used to organize names that all start with the same letter, or paintings that are all done by the same artist. Sections are helpful because they organize your content and with table view controllers, can be used with an index where the user can jump to different sections.}